<p><i>  General observations: 
</i></p>
<p>44. The Special Rapporteur regrets that the Government of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
</p>
<p>has not responded to seven communications sent during the reporting period. In the absence 
</p>
<p>of a response and clarification on the cases addressed therein and given the irreversible 
</p>
<p>nature of capital punishment, the Special Rapporteur urges the Government to take all 
</p>
<p>necessary measures to prevent the execution of the subjects of these communications. 
</p>
