</i></p>
<p>48. The Special Rapporteur thanks the Government of Israel for its substantive reply to 
</p>
<p>the communication of 28 August 2014 and encourages the Israeli authorities to provide 
</p>
<p>substantive responses to the two others communications mentioned above.  The Special 
</p>
<p>Rapporteur is concern regarding the alleged excessive use of force used against these 
</p>
<p>protesters by Israeli security forces. Therefore, he calls upon the Government of Israel to 
</p>
<p>send information on the regulations and operational procedures for law enforcement agents 
</p>
<p>concerning the use of force in the context of law enforcement during assemblies and 
</p>
