</p>
<p>responses. The Special Rapporteur calls on the Government to take all necessary measures 
</p>
<p>to create a safe and enabling environment for human rights defenders and journalists to </p>

<p><b>A/HRC/29/37/Add.5 
</b></p>
<p> <b>49 
</b></p>
<p>carry out their legitimate activities without the fear of being killed. He stresses that in all 
</p>
<p>suspected cases of extrajudicial, summary or arbitrary executions shall be a prompt, 
</p>
