</p>
<p>its response. In its reply, the Government indicates that after exhausting the domestic 
</p>
<p>judicial processes, Messrs. Zaniar Moradi and Loghman Moradi have been convicted to 
</p>
<p>death penalty by the court. The Special urges the Government to ensure that death penalty 
</p>
<p>safeguards are fully respected in all capital punishment cases.  
